topics.body:
Take, O Moon, I pray thee, take me,
Take me, thou, O Sun above me,
Take me, thou O Bear of heaven,
From this dark and dreary prison,
From these unbefitting portals,
From this narrow place of resting,
From this dark and gloomy dwelling,
Hence to wander from the ocean,
Hence to walk upon the islands,
On the dry land walk and wander,
Like an ancient hero wander,
Walk in open air and breathe it,
Thus to see the moon at evening,
Thus to see the silver sunlight,
Thus to see the Bear in heaven,
That the stars I may consider.

BI is a bit hard to understand with all the wibbly wobbly timey wimey thing happening all around but then, you reach an epiphany and realize the truth.

In short, it has something to do with alternate universes and killing someone which leads to the non-existence of a single constant from the ever existing multiverse due to a grudge and potential danger. To destroy the enemy before he even began but was revealed that Booker is Commstock but from an alternate universe and they fight over that one girl which is Booker's daughter known as Elizabeth. So to kill Commstock and his potential danger to the world, she killed Booker before he became Commstock.
